quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Multiple Parameters  [/h1]

When calling the function, provide the arguments in the same order in which you defined them.[code format="js" codeId="679"]function sayHello(name, age) {
  document.write( name + " is " + age + " years old.");
}

sayHello([b]"John", 20[/b])
//Outputs "John is 20 years old."[/code]
